---
title: Easy Beef Rump & Lemony Potatoes with Tomato Salad & Hollandaise
description: A mashed potato is a classic but wouldn’t it be fun if we tried something a little different tonight? Why not crush the potatoes instead with a squeeze of lemon juice for extra zap. They’ll go nicely with the seasoned beef rump, drizzled in hollandaise. This will become the only way you’ll want your potatoes and beef.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

